---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroImg from '../components/HeroImg.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import heroImg from '../images/support/wph-support.webp';
import sonyPonyImg from '../images/support/sonyPonyUlices.webp'
---

<Layout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>Support — Wedding Photo Hangover</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://weddinghangover.com/support/" />
    <meta name="description" content="Support Us On Patreon" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Wedding Photo Hangover - A Wedding Photography Podcast" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Support — Wedding Photo Hangover" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Support Us On Patreon" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://weddinghangover.com/support" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/images/global/WPH_Wide_CleanNB.webp" />
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="1500" />
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="843" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Support — Wedding Photo Hangover" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Support Us On Patreon" />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/images/global/WPH_Wide_CleanNB.webp" />
    <meta name="twitter:url" content="https://weddinghangover.com/support" />
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Support — Wedding Photo Hangover" />
    <meta itemprop="description" content="Support Us On Patreon" />
    <meta itemprop="url" content="https://weddinghangover.com/support" />
    <meta itemprop="image" content="/images/global/WPH_Wide_CleanNB.webp" />
  </Fragment>

  <main>
    <HeroImg 
      title="You Already Love Us, So Why Not Support Us?" 
      background={heroImg}
    />
    <div class="content-container">
        <section>
            <h1 style="text-align:center">Top Ways You Can Support the Wedding Photo Hangover Podcast and Blog:</h1>
        </section>

        <section class="card-support">
            <div class="card-content">
                <a href="https://www.patreon.com/WPH" class="button-link">Sign Up On Patreon</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <a href="https://amzn.to/3uKrH3u" class="button-link">Shop on Amazon</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <a href="https://www.zazzle.com/store/weddinghangover" class="button-link">Buy Our Swag</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Patreon</h2>
            <p>Your support of this podcast by listening and sharing episodes means so much to us. Thanks. But you want to know what we like more than your undying support? Your hard earned, cash money. Tap the “<a href="https://www.patreon.com/WPH" target="_blank">Sign Up On Patreon</a>” button above to sign up for our Patreon and get access to a bunch of content we locked away behind a paywall.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Wanna Buy Cool Stuff?</h2>
            <p>We have a <a href="https://www.zazzle.com/mbr/238859053052963435/collections">Zazzle Store</a> and a <a href="https://teechip.com/SonyPony">TeeChip store</a> where you can find cool shirts, beer bottle openers, wine stoppers, and more.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <Image
                src={sonyPonyImg}
                alt="You could look as cool as Ulices Del Toro!"
                style="max-width:100%; height:auto;"
                format="webp"
                quality={80}
            />
            <p style="text-align:center;">You could look as cool as <a href="http://www.deltorophoto.com/">Ulices Del Toro</a>!</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Ratings and Reviews</h2>
            <p>If you can’t support us monetarily, but you still want to show us some love, you can leave us a five star review. We prefer reviews on iTunes, but would love reviews anywhere you can leave them. Here are some links if you want to put your love of the podcast on display for the whole world to see:</p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/wedding-photo-hangover/id1273248325?mt=2" target="_blank">iTunes</a>, 
                <a href="https://www.podchaser.com/podcasts/wedding-photo-hangover-561241" target="_blank">Podchaser</a>, 
                <a href="https://www.podbean.com/podcast-detail/gu8hf-60cff/Wedding-Photo-Hangover-Podcast" target="_blank">Podbean</a>, 
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/WeddingPhotoHangover/" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
        <h2>Social Sharing</h2>
        <p>Still not content with all the ways to support us? We don’t deserve you. But if you want another way to help us out, we’d appreciate you sharing the podcast with your friends and family. Look, we need all the help we can get proselytizing people everywhere. So, go into your podcast app of choice, grab a share link, and then just post the coolest thing you can think of to social media that’ll make all your cool friends and family thirsty for this podcast. Are we a thirst trap? We’re trying to be. It’s part of our plan to become the best photography podcast in the known universe. When you do share the podcast, tag us in your post so we can thank you for being so awesome. If you want to share an episode to your Instagram story, we recommend using <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/09hCjT9XXAKzGin8bkLG3a?si=yJ1LWKZxTySgeDcfQtFvDQ" target="_blank">Spotify</a>, because then people can tap that “Play on Spotify” link in the top left of your story and get instant access to our dulcet tones.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
        <h2 style="text-align:center">Thanks so much for all of your support!</h2>
        </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>